== 西元前 ==
*西元前2560年–860年：埃及的工匠拋光[[水晶|水晶]]、[[寶石|半寶石]]和晚期用[[玻璃|玻璃]]為[[木乃伊|木乃伊]]和[[雕塑|雕塑]]製作惟妙惟肖的眼睛。似乎意圖產生一種幻覺<ref>{{cite journal |author=Enoch J |title=First known lenses originating in Egypt about 4600 years ago! |journal=Hindsight |volume=31 |issue=2 |pages=9–17 |pmid=11624467 |date=April 2000}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.io.cfmac.csic.es/PDFs/Semi_IyV/seminario_enoch.PDF#search=%22Egyptian%20rock%20crystal%20lens%20illusion%22 |title=Studies of the oldest Known Lenses at the Louvre (4600 Years Before the Present) |access-date=2011-06-17 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172632/http://www.io.cfmac.csic.es/PDFs/Semi_IyV/seminario_enoch.PDF#search=%22Egyptian%20rock%20crystal%20lens%20illusion%22 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://home.comcast.net/~hebsed/enoch.htm |title=Remarkable Old Kingdom Lenses and the Illusion of the Following Eye |access-date=2011-06-17 |archive-date=2015-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002125933/http://home.comcast.net/~hebsed/enoch.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
*西元前470年–390年：中國的哲學家[[墨子|墨子]]寫出使用凹面鏡可以聚集陽光{{Citation needed|date=October 2007}}。
*西元前424 年：[[阿里斯托芬|阿里斯托芬]]''透鏡''是裝滿水的玻璃球 ([[塞尼加|塞尼加]]說：''不論多小或多暗的字都可以用它來閱讀''。) <ref>{{harvnb|King|2003|p=[http://books.google.com/books?id=KAWwzHlDVksC&pg=PA25 25]}}</ref>。
*西元前3世紀：[[歐基里德|歐基里德]]是第一位寫下光線的直線傳播、折射、反射和註解。<ref>{{harvnb|King|2003|p=[http://books.google.com/books?id=KAWwzHlDVksC&pg=PA26 26]}}</ref>。

